1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,920
Makoto, you really know your stuff.

2
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:08,970
For the School Festival Prince contest,
you've definitely got my vote!

3
00:00:08,970 --> 00:00:11,510
Natsu, you've had too much to drink.
You're cut off!

4
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:15,020
- Hey, give it back!
- No way! I said you're done!

5
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,600
You're completely wasted.

6
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,400
- I'm not drunk! Seriously!
- No, really. I told you, you've had enough.

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,810
I'm serious.

8
00:00:22,810 --> 00:00:24,820
- Huh?
- I'm going to the bathroom.

9
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:27,650
Hey, you're not gonna puke, are you?
Promise me you won't puke.

10
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:30,070
(What's with them?
All that flirting...)

11
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:32,740
All that flirting... you two must be pretty close.

12
00:00:32,740 --> 00:00:33,870
We are not.

13
00:00:33,870 --> 00:00:37,040
If that's not flirting,
then what is?

14
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:40,370
You're not jealous, are you?

15
00:00:40,370 --> 00:00:42,960
Well then, maybe we should
do a little flirting of our own?

16
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,340
Alright then.

17
00:00:45,170 --> 00:00:47,840
Hey, cut it out.
Don't suddenly go all 'Popular' on me.

18
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:50,510
Yeah, I guess I had a phase like that.

19
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:52,640
I don't hang out with that crowd anymore.

20
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,140
You mean the 'Popular clique'?

21
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:57,560
Yeah.
It's more fun hanging out with you, Makoto.

22
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:01,480
Well, I have a pretty good time
with you too.

23
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:05,480
Uh-oh.
I think I might be drunk.

24
00:01:10,110 --> 00:01:11,320
Makoto...

25
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,450
Hm?
